* Task 6 fixture: INCLUDE extraction
* Contains two INCLUDE statements: one quoted and one unquoted.
* Natural allows both forms.
* Copycode targets are treated as literal names regardless of quoting.

DEFINE DATA
LOCAL
  1 REQUEST-REC
    2 REQUEST-ID (A10)
END DEFINE

INCLUDE 'COMMON-DECLS'

INCLUDE ERRHANDLER

MOVE 'REQ001' TO REQUEST-ID

END
